<h2>Facts</h2>

Today is {{dayOfWeek}}. There are normally bikes available on {{dayOfWeek}} {{h-percent dayOfWeekPercent}} of the time.
<br>
It's about {{nearestFifteenDisplay}}. There are normally bikes available {{h-percent nearestFifteenPercent}} of the time.
<br>
This station is in service {{h-percent inServicePercent}} of the time.
<br>
When it's in the {{degreesInTens}}°s, there are normally bikes {{h-percent degreesInTensPercent}} of the time.
<br>
When it's {{currentWeather.summary}}, there are normally bikes {{h-percent summaryPercent}} of the time.

<h2>Prediction</h2>

<h3>There's a {{h-percent pHasBikes}} chance there will be bikes at {{model.station.location}}</h3>

<h3>Math</h3>

<code>
  P(dayOfWeek = {{dayOfWeek}} | hasBikes = true) = {{h-percent pDayOfWeekTrue}}
  <br>
  P(timeOfDay = {{nearestFifteenDisplay}} | hasBikes = true) = {{h-percent pTimeOfDayTrue}}
  <br>
  P(degrees = {{degreesInTens}}°s | hasBikes = true) = {{h-percent pDegreesTrue}}
  <br>
  P(conditions = {{currentWeather.summary}} | hasBikes = true) = {{h-percent pSummaryTrue}}
  <br>
</code>

<br>

<code>
  P(dayOfWeek = {{dayOfWeek}} | hasBikes = false) = {{h-percent pDayOfWeekFalse}}
  <br>
  P(timeOfDay = {{nearestFifteenDisplay}} | hasBikes = false) = {{h-percent pTimeOfDayFalse}}
  <br>
  P(degrees = {{degreesInTens}}°s | hasBikes = false) = {{h-percent pDegreesFalse}}
  <br>
  P(conditions = {{currentWeather.summary}} | hasBikes = false) = {{h-percent pSummaryFalse}}
  <br>
</code>

<br>

<code>
  P({{dayOfWeek}} | true) P({{nearestFifteenDisplay}} | true) P({{degreesInTens}}°s | true) P({{currentWeather.summary}} | true) = {{h-percent pTotalTrue}}
  <br>
  P({{dayOfWeek}} | false) P({{nearestFifteenDisplay}} | false) P({{degreesInTens}}°s | false) P({{currentWeather.summary}} | false) = {{h-percent pTotalFalse}}
  <br>
  {{h-percent pTotalTrue}} / ({{h-percent pTotalTrue}} + {{h-percent pTotalFalse}}) = {{h-percent pHasBikes}}
</code>

